mraa (2.0.0-3) buster; urgency=medium

  * fixed Rock Pi 4 on recent 5.x kernels
  * added function file_contains_case_sensitive
  * nodejs-dev is no longer available
  * switched to clang as compiler
  * added mraa-uart to mraa-tools
  * fixed build as patch seems not to patch CMakeList.txt anymore, so as 
    temporary solution disabled the building of docs

 -- Carsten Menke <cm@p-i-u.de>  Tue, 27 Sep 2019 23:47:37 +0000

